						<summary>

						<p>This inscription states that stone enclosure was built around spring besides cleaned and maintained by Pārambaiyūruḍaiyāṉ Poṉṉāṇḍār Tirukkaivēlaḻagiyār, a native of Sundarachōḻapuram <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Dēsiyugandapaṭṭaṇam in Ollaiyūr kūṟṟam.</p>						

